lead_paragraph: Chelsea's clash with Premier League title rivals Manchester City will not define their season and the games against lesser teams will be more significant, goalkeeper Thibaut Courtois said.

headline.print_headline: City Game Not the Acid Test for Chelsea, Says Courtois
headline.main: City Game Not the Acid Test for Chelsea, Says Courtois
